Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveThe Ebem Ohafia community in Ohafia Local Government Area of Abia State is being threatened by gully erosion.
Houses in the community, including the palace of the monarch, HRH Ukoha Kalu Ukoha, is at risk of collapsing due to erosion.
The President General of Ebem Ohafia Development Union, Mr. Emeka Mba, urged the Federal Ministries of Works, Environment and other relevant authorities to intervene in the matter.
